{"tid":2131375,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國巨石陣源頭揭開","createTime":"2020-07-29T22:52:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T00:46:11.000Z","uid":348984,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"825054f5bde1d04ecaea8e6c11d946dcc9e9d650","tid":2131375,"uid":348984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T22:52:32.000Z","msg":"位於英格蘭埃姆斯伯里的巨石陣來自何處一直未明，考古學界今日披露了關鍵的直立巨石來源。<br />\n<br />\n一項今日刊登在《科學》雜誌旗下期刊的研究披露，巨石陣中直立的巨石來自巨石陣往北 25 公里，位於威爾特郡的一個叢林。<br />\n<br />\n研究取得突破的關鍵，是在 1958 年考古中被取走的柱心，於六十年後被歸還。團隊使用了 X 光，並通過電感耦合等離子體分析柱心的化學元素，確認來源的確吻合。<br />\n<br />\n而早前的研究則顯示，巨石陣中較小的「青石」，是搬運自威爾斯的普瑞斯里山。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://advances.sciencemag.org/content/6/31/eabc0133\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fadvances.sciencemag.org%2Fcontent%2F6%2F31%2Feabc0133&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhBFNIXSBonesC3SPsSCGYVE%3D&h=79f75ece\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://advances.sciencemag.org/content/6/31/eabc0133</a>"},{"pid":"9a32d14481c5d00ed913f55b193b411a7197695d","tid":2131375,"uid":231583,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T23:14:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0af82c7276480e793013d0a081518a8cc7419b09","tid":2131375,"uid":191926,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9a32d14481c5d00ed913f55b193b411a7197695d","tid":2131375,"uid":231583,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T23:14:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T23:20:12.000Z","msg":"無<br />\n可能近看會好少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n幾十米外看 只是一堆爛石<br />\n<br />\n果陣報左 Kk day 三大景點"},{"pid":"f4e734be702827d57a375eea9972515fbd04fe93","tid":2131375,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0af82c7276480e793013d0a081518a8cc7419b09","tid":2131375,"uid":191926,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9a32d14481c5d00ed913f55b193b411a7197695d","tid":2131375,"uid":231583,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyT